        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Constitutional Amendment - Grants Congress the power to set limits on the amounts of contributions and expenditures with respect to candidates in a federal election.</p> <p>Grants a state the power to set limits on the amounts of contributions and expenditures with respect to candidates in a state or local election.</p>]]></text>
